                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0x854A75D5<!--String: "Raheel and I used to get along well when we were kids, but I just find his whole free-wheeling "bit" tedious. I'm all about order. There's a reason I'm a Camp Director: I keep things going on schedule the way they're supposed to. Sims who want to do their own thing are just oddballs. "--></T>
